About

This is the unofficial ranking of  WGI-bound ensembles   through the season. Rankings are purely based on scores from regionals across the country, and do not reflect any official rankings by  WGI . Since scores and judges vary by regional, this is not meant to be an accurate representation of the rankings going into  WGI finals , just a loose idea of where each ensemble stands. The score shown is the unit's latest total score (with penalties).
